193">HK$23,193 raised</span><span class="progress-bar__goal" data-goal="HK$200,000">HK$200,000 goal</span></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col col--5   "><div class="col__container css-lpwily"></div></div></div></section><section class="row row--2 row--align-none row__layout--section css-12wvcv3" id="row--2" style="background-color: rgb(251, 179, 22);"><div class="row__bg" style="background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; opacity: 1;"></div><div class="row__container"><div class="col col--6   "><div class="col__container css-1my0da"><p class="css-6alne6" style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Commemorating Mahatma Gandhi's 150th year Birth Anniversary </strong></em><strong>Woodlands Indian Vegetarian Restaurant is organizing their Annual Charity Lunch &amp; Dinner on the 7th October (MON - Public Holiday) </strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong>EAT AS MUCH AS YOU CAN &amp; PAY AS MUCH AS YOU WISH</strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Lunch : 11:30am - 3:30pm &amp; Dinner : 6:30pm to 10:30pm</strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p></div></div><div class="col col--6   "><div class="col__container css-1029ksm"><p class="css-1pe3lbi" style="text-align: center;"><strong>SILENCE - is a Hong Kong based Charity Organization serving the people with hearing &amp; speaking disability. All donations received through this event will be donated to SILENCE. For more information on their operation, see the video below.</strong></p><p class="css-1bsgdjo" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p><p class="css-1bsgdjo" style="text-align: center;"><strong></strong></p></div></div></div></section><section class="row row--3 row--align-center row__layout--section css-hetghf" id="row--3"><div class="row__bg" style="background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; opacity: 1;"></div><div class="row__container"><div class="col col--12   "><div class="col__container css-1jfa07k"><p class="css-1th5cut" style="color: rgb(27, 19, 222);">                            <strong>Tax exemption is available for donations of HK$100 or more. Tax redemption receipt will be sent to your e-mail.</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section class="row row--4 row--align-none row__layout--section css-lv3wzn" id="row--4" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(141, 199, 73);"><div class="row__bg" style="background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; opacity: 1;"></div><div class="row__container"><div class="col col--7   "><div class="col__container css-1gabuuw"><div class="raisely-blockwrapper raisely-blockwrapper--video css-tuc5tu"><div class="video-wrapper"><iframe title="undefined-video" width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-uA52GHp17U?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;autoplay=0" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen="true" mozallowfullscreen="true" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></div><p class="css-tz3rbf" style="text-align: right;"><em>    </em></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: right;"><strong><em>From the year 1985 till 2004, Woodlands Indian Vegetarian Restaurant had conducted Charity Lunch &amp; Dinner on every year October and raised over $850,000 and donated to Oxfam, Orbis, Medicin Sans Frontier, Cancer Foundation, Children's Cancer Foundation, The Hong Kong Cancer Fund, Kwun Tong Resident Association, CRY Children Relief &amp; You, Yan Chai Hospital and Community Chest in Hong Kong. </em></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej"><em></em></p><p class="css-xznnej"><strong><em>從1985年到2004年，活蘭印度素食餐廳每年10月進行慈善午餐和晚餐，籌集了超過85萬元，並捐贈給了樂施會，奧比斯，無國界醫生，癌症基金會，兒童癌症基金會，香港癌症基金會，觀塘居民協會，CRY兒童救濟與您組織，香港仁濟醫院和公益金。</em></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej"><em></em></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: right;"><em>    </em><strong><em>The Charity event has been restored after 14 years and this year we have planned to do it in a bigger scale with not only on-site donation, but also online. We request individuals to contribute generously towards this cause so as to maximize the donation and be a part of a change in the society, to build a harmonious and barrier-free world.</em></strong></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: right;"><em></em></p><p class="css-xznnej" style="text-align: right;"><strong><em>十四年後的今天，慈善活動終終恢復，今年，我們計劃通過現場捐贈和網上捐贈來擴大規模。 我們需要每位為這次活動作出慷慨的捐助，令捐款數字節節上升，可以幫助到更多有需要人士，以建立一個和諧，無障礙的世界。</em></strong></p><div class="raisely-blockwrapper raisely-blockwrapper--custom-component css-1uns6qn"><div class="share share--filled share--medium"><a title="Share" href="http://facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fannualcharity.woodlandshk.com%2F" target="_blank" class="share-button share-button--filled share-button--medium share-button--facebook"><i data-icon-name="mdiFacebook"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon icon--default icon--medium icon--id-facebook "><path d="M17,2V2H17V6H15C14.31,6 14,6.81 14,7.5V10H14L17,10V14H14V22H10V14H7V10H10V6C10,3.79 11.79,2 14,2H17Z"></path></svg></i><span class="share-button__label">Share</span></a><a title="Tweet" href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fannualcharity.woodlandshk.com%2F&amp;text=Annual%20Charity%20Lunch%20%26%20Dinner%20-%20Woodlands%20Indian%20Vegetarian%20Restaurant%20%3A%20Make%20a%20donation%20today%20to%20support%20Annual%20Charity%20Lunch%20%26%20Dinner%20-%20Woodlands%20Indian%20Vegetarian%20Restaurant&amp;hashtags=annual-charity-lunch-and-dinner-woodlands-indian-vegetarian-restaurant&amp;via=raisely" target="_blank" class="share-button share-button--filled share-button--medium sh